msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga → sambodhivaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn48.61:0.2"
msgid "7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga"
msgstr "7. Leading to Awakening"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.61:0.3"
msgid "61. Saṃyojanasutta"
msgstr "61. Fetters"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.61:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. </p><p class="added">
#. VAR: saṃyojanappahānāya → saññojanānaṃ pahānāya (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn48.61:1.2"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni bhāvitāni bahulīkatāni saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these five faculties are developed and cultivated they lead to giving up the fetters."

msgctxt "sn48.61:1.3"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.61:1.4"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ—"
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.61:1.5"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcindriyāni bhāvitāni bahulīkatāni saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr "When these five faculties are developed and cultivated they lead to giving up the fetters.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.61:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
